{"anchor_hash": "510e8112856ba7277986984212a512399d6a4007dcbd33fdf56b8eec0d321bdd", "app_version": "review-interface-v0-scratchpad-1", "approximate_scroll_percent": null, "chapter_id": null, "chapter_title": null, "comment_text": "Writing style - try to be subtle when including world building stuff instead of beating the reader over the head with it, especially when it comes to moralistic statements etc - what would the character actually be thinking, as someone who’s used to the situation?", "commenter_name": "DustinR", "content_hash": "13d00f2d9dfdf49e4c356dfbd3d4c074c19b06457175d59faa416338946f82ef", "created_at": "2026-06-28T18:20:11.946Z", "current_file_path": null, "current_heading": "Technical / Processing", "current_layer": "author-scratchpad", "id": "scratchpad-1782670811946-3rhhwk", "import_batch_id": "2026-06-29-001", "imported_at": "2026-06-29T19:49:35+00:00", "importer_version": "webapp-comment-import-v1", "initial_classification": "scratchpad-technical", "likely_target_id": "technical-processing", "likely_target_type": "scratchpad", "normalized_id": "wc-13d00f2d9dfdf49e", "processing_status": "imported", "repo_branch": "beta", "repo_commit": "c21bc35941773c840d3a2d3569e8200a116d8d30", "reviewer_session_id": "session-432bfb71-a607-43b9-bd28-0a47756c139f", "scratchpad_type": "technical-processing", "selected_text": null, "source_export_file": "fractured-fate-comments-dustinr-20260629-1416-from-drive.json", "source_line_end": null, "source_line_start": null, "status": "inbox", "view_mode": "scratchpad"}
{"anchor_hash": "6822f89d52837ee81842c6b6cae7cba9a234d070ab9632da61e7fa94be3fa1dd", "app_version": "review-interface-v0-scratchpad-1", "approximate_scroll_percent": null, "chapter_id": null, "chapter_title": null, "comment_text": "To Davian - did you really think that after all these years in the shadows you could come out with her into the light? - Kelyra isn’t very happy he wants to go help Maya after they kill Serathis. Sets Kelyra up as an antagonist in later books, wanting to kill Maya \n\nMaya would have done some admin work before presentation and been familiar with it, but now she is doing it more public-facing. Think transition from med student to resident \n\nSorevin didn’t have any children who could Shroud, certainly none that could be Presented (at a Low Clade Presentation where high clades generally wouldn’t deign to attend except for the master of ceremonies). So when he dies Maya wants to bring someone from his house in that survived but Niall lets her know that’s not how it works, but they could join another proxy low Clade & Maya could designate that one as the new contract handlers\n\nNiall to Maya after presentation- you have no idea of the political ramifications of what you did.", "commenter_name": "DustinR", "content_hash": "2a115febc9c7a43b240ff2428a70bc10f46f122e2e4bf9c36f15687d1e38643a", "created_at": "2026-06-28T18:20:33.833Z", "current_file_path": null, "current_heading": "Content", "current_layer": "author-scratchpad", "id": "scratchpad-1782670833833-xjex54", "import_batch_id": "2026-06-29-001", "imported_at": "2026-06-29T19:49:35+00:00", "importer_version": "webapp-comment-import-v1", "initial_classification": "scratchpad-content", "likely_target_id": "content", "likely_target_type": "scratchpad", "normalized_id": "wc-2a115febc9c7a43b", "processing_status": "imported", "repo_branch": "beta", "repo_commit": "c21bc35941773c840d3a2d3569e8200a116d8d30", "reviewer_session_id": "session-432bfb71-a607-43b9-bd28-0a47756c139f", "scratchpad_type": "content", "selected_text": null, "source_export_file": "fractured-fate-comments-dustinr-20260629-1416-from-drive.json", "source_line_end": null, "source_line_start": null, "status": "inbox", "view_mode": "scratchpad"}
